snippet.title: Arcane Legends Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Arcane Legends is the latest game from Spacetime Studios available now on the App Store and Google Play! 

Get ready for a new Co-Op Action RPG with a fun and refreshing take on fantasy. In a lush, beautifully rendered world, players customize their hero, collect and develop animal companions, and adventure with friends from all around the world!

Arcane Legends: http://www.arcanelegendsgame.com/
Spacetime Studios: http://www.spacetimestudios.com/
